    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis has been vetted for subframe integrity, and the double-VANOS system has been serviced to ensure precise cam timing. While showing minor road wear indicative of its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and suspension damping remain tight, offering an authentic analog performance experience.",
